<sect1 id="dir_9c6cd3e8e6e0499e50b91381009c10c7_1autotoc_md234">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::lifecycle::components</title><para>Components for managing entity lifecycle states.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9c6cd3e8e6e0499e50b91381009c10c7_1autotoc_md235">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides components that track and manage the activation state of other components on an entity. The primary use case is delayed activation after spawn.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9c6cd3e8e6e0499e50b91381009c10c7_1autotoc_md236">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="2" cols="2"><row>
